
'''The Gods must be Crazy''' ni film yo gusetsa yo mu 1980 yanditswe, yakozwe, itunganywa kandi iyobowe na Jamie Uys<ref>https://www.nytimes.com/1985/04/28/movies/the-gods-must-be-crazy-a-truly-international-hit.html</ref> . ubufatanyabikorwa mpuzamahanga muri Afrika yepfo na Botswana, ni film yambere muri '''The Gods must be Crazy''' series <ref>https://www.nytimes.com/1984/10/28/arts/film-view-is-the-gods-must-be-crazy-only-a-comedy.html</ref>.

Iyi filime yashyizwe muri Afurika y'Epfo, ikinamo umuhinzi wo muri Namibiya San Nǃxau ǂToma nka Xi<ref>https://www.hotstar.com/id/movies/the-gods-must-be-crazy/1260058358</ref>, umuhigi-uhiga mu butayu bwa Kalahari umuryango we wavumbuye icupa ry'ikirahure ryamanutse mu ndege, kandi bizera ko ari impano yatanzwe n'imana zabo<ref>https://www.egypttoday.com/Article/4/40901/African-comedy-%E2%80%9CThe-Gods-Must-Be-Crazy%E2%80%9D-to-screen-at</ref>. Igihe Xi yiyemeje gusubiza icupa ku mana, urugendo rwe ruba ruhujwe n’umuhanga mu binyabuzima (wakinnye nka Marius Weyers )<ref>https://www.classification.gov.au/titles/gods-must-be-crazy-0</ref>, umwarimu w’ishuri ry’umudugudu mushya ( Sandra Prinsloo ), hamwe n’itsinda ry’iterabwoba<ref>https://www.classiccinemas.com.au/movies/saffa19-the-gods-must-be-crazy</ref> .

'''''The Gods must be Crazy'''''  yarekuwe na Ster-Kinekor muri Afrika yepfo, aho yakoze amateka yinjiza amafaranga menshi<ref>https://www.britannica.com/topic/The-Gods-Must-Be-Crazy</ref>, ikaba yarasohoye amafaranga menshi mumateka yinganda za firime za Afrika yepfo<ref>https://www.boxofficemojo.com/release/rl1163167233/weekend/</ref>.  Iyi filime yagenze neza mu bucuruzi no mu bindi bihugu, harimo na Leta zunze ubumwe z’Amerika<ref>https://www.cram.com/essay/Symbolism-In-The-Gods-Must-Be-Crazy/PKV5BMH9J5XW</ref>, aho yatanzwe na 20 Century Fox, aho ibiganiro [[Ikinyafurikansi|by’umwimerere bya Afrikaans]] yashyizwe mu cyongereza<ref>https://www.alamy.com/stock-photo/the-gods-must-be-crazy.html</ref>. Nubwo byagenze neza, iyi filime yakunze kunengwa kwerekana ubwoko kandi bigaragara ko atazi ivangura  muri Afurika yepfo<ref>https://www.washingtonpost.com/archive/lifestyle/1984/11/02/the-gods-must-be-crazy/07fb5c2e-8f81-4aba-90bd-e36e47d3438f/</ref>. Film yakurikiwe ni ikindi gice  '''The Gods must be Crazy''' part II  yashyizwe ahagaragara Columbia Pictures mu 1989.<ref>https://www.tandfonline.com/doi/pdf/10.1080/08949460600598711</ref> 

=== Gufata amashusho ===
''The Gods Must Be Crazy yafatiwe amashusho'' i Tsumkwe, muri Namibiya,  ndetse no muri Botswana. <ref>https://moviesanywhere.com/movie/the-gods-must-be-crazy</ref>Nk’uko Uys abitangaza ngo N! Xau yasubizwaga mu rugo rwe mu butayu bwa Kalahari buri byumweru bitatu cyangwa bine kugira ngo atababazwa n’umuco<ref>https://www.scmp.com/yp/discover/entertainment/movies/article/3065554/vault-gods-must-be-crazy-full-laughs-and-life</ref> .  Mu gihe mu mijyi, N! Xau yize kunywa inzoga n'itabi. <ref>https://www.fnac.com/mp3063455/The-Gods-Must-Be-Crazy-Gods-Must-Be-Crazy-2</ref> Uys yavuze ko yishyuye N! Xau $ 300 mu minsi 10 ya mbere yakoraga, ariko ko amafaranga bivugwa ko yatwawe n'umuyaga<ref>https://mercycollegefilmandculture.com/2019/02/01/thematic-elements-and-tone-in-the-gods-must-be-crazy-and-dust-devil/</ref>.  N! Xau yahise yishyurwa n'inka 12. <ref>https://www.tvguide.com/movies/the-gods-must-be-crazy/tv-listings/2030277302/</ref> Mu 1985, Uys yavuze ko yohereje N! Xau $ 100 buri kwezi kuva yafata amashusho, N! Xau yakoresheje mu iduka ry’ubucuruzi ku bilometero 60 uvuye aho yahigaga<ref>https://scienceonscreen.org/films/the-gods-must-be-crazy</ref>; Uys yavuze kandi ko hashyizweho konti y’amadolari 20.000 y’izina rya N! Xau.<ref>https://www.spiritualityandpractice.com/films/reviews/view/8639</ref>   

== Controversies ==
''The Gods Must Be Crazy'' yakunze kunengwa kubera ko bigaragara ko ikomeje imyumvire ishingiye ku moko n'ivangura n'ivangura muri Afurika y'Epfo<ref>https://igihe.com/sagatwa</ref>.  Muri Amerika, ngo iyi filime yatowe n’inama y’igihugu y’abavoka b’abirabura n’indi mitwe irwanya ivanguramoko ubwo yerekanaga mu nzu ya Street Street ya 68 mu mujyi wa New York. <ref>https://ukwezi.rw/Imyidagaduro/article/Ibitangaje-wamenya-kuri-N%C7%83xau-%C7%82Toma-Sagatwa-wishwe-n-igituntu</ref>

